   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "## Validation\n\n`res1`/`res0` vs. direct `Residue[f[u,n,S1,S2,w], {u,1}]` / `{u,0}`, for the new denominator `u^(2 S1) (u-1)^(2 S2)`: pole at `u=1` has order `2 S2`, pole at `u=0` has order `2 S1`. Swept over `n ∈ {0,...,4}`, `S1 ∈ {0,...,4}`, `S2 ∈ {1,...,4}` for `res1` and `S2 ∈ {0,...,4}` for `res0` (S2=0 has no pole at u=1; `res1` has no guard for that edge case, unlike `res0`'s `If[2 S1>n,...,0]`). All mismatches = 0.",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "mismatches1 = Reap[\n   Do[\n    diff = Simplify[res1[n, S1, S2] - Residue[mm[u, n, S1, S2, w], {u, 1}]];\n    If[diff =!= 0, Sow[{n, S1, S2, diff}]],\n    {n, 0, 4}, {S1, 0, 4}, {S2, 1, 4}\n    ]\n   ][[2]] // Flatten[#, 1] &;\nmismatches0 = Reap[\n   Do[\n    diff = Simplify[res0[n, S1, S2] - Residue[mm[u, n, S1, S2, w], {u, 0}]];\n    If[diff =!= 0, Sow[{n, S1, S2, diff}]],\n    {n, 0, 4}, {S1, 0, 4}, {S2, 0, 4}\n    ]\n   ][[2]] // Flatten[#, 1] &;\nPrint[\"mismatches (res1, res0) = \", {Length[mismatches1], Length[mismatches0]}];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-print-output\"><div class=\"wl-print-line\"><span class=\"wl-ps\">mismatches (res1, res0) = </span><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrvouxcz-y2tz1fu\" data-page-width-em=\"26\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRcezAsMFxyaWdodFx9\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Print: mismatches (res1, res0) =[formula]",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "29bbd1a8-bd4e-489f-9e95-6fa61b596cb1"
    }
